quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,The emulous desire of multiplying riches and children employeth you
  102,2,until ye visit the graves
  102,3,"By no means should ye thus employ your time: Hereafter shall ye know your folly"
  102,4,"Again, by no means: Hereafter shall ye know your folly"
  102,5,"By no means: If ye knew the consequence hereof with certainty of knowledge, ye would not act thus"
  102,6,Verily ye shall see hell
  102,7,"Again, ye shall surely see it with the eye of certainty"
  102,8,"Then shall ye be examined, on that day, concerning the pleasures with which ye have amused yourselves in this life"